745
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:09,960
I'm so sad.

746
00:42:11,480 --> 00:42:12,520
If I'd known this before,

747
00:42:12,880 --> 00:42:14,560
I wouldn't flatter myself

748
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:19,040
