What's this?

750
00:42:24,080 --> 00:42:25,280
See for yourself.

751
00:42:32,360 --> 00:42:32,920
This...

752
00:42:40,560 --> 00:42:41,320
How shameless!

753
00:42:41,560 --> 00:42:42,320
I'm so pissed off.

